  "html": "<div class=\"fr-view\">\n<p><strong>REVISION CRAM SHEETS</strong></p>\n<p>Most students struggle at first with knowing how to correctly use particles and interrogatives correctly. Please see the below cram sheets with the words and phrases you have learned so far and how to use the interrogatives and particles correctly.</p>\n<p><strong>PARTICLES</strong></p>\n<p>Japanese particles, joshi (助詞) or tenioha (てにをは), are short words in Japanese grammar that immediately follow a noun, verb, adjective, or sentence to help give meaning and context. </p>\n<p><img src=\"../../images/shared/Screen_Shot_2020-06-02_at_11.14.26.png\" style=\"width: auto; max-width: 100%; height: auto;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" srcset=\"../../images/shared/Screen_Shot_2020-06-02_at_11.14.26.png?width=1920 1x, ../../images/shared/Screen_Shot_2020-06-02_at_11.14.26.png?width=1920&amp;dpr=2 2x, ../../images/shared/Screen_Shot_2020-06-02_at_11.14.26.png?width=1920&amp;dpr=3 3x\"></p>\n<p>You can also download this information here:<strong>  </strong><a class=\"fr-file\" href=\"../../pdfs/shared/particle_(2).pdf\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>particle.pdf</strong></a></p>\n<p><strong>INTERROGATIVES</strong></p>\n<p>An <em>interrogative</em> sentence asks a direct question (Who, What, When, Where, Which) and is punctuated at the end with the question marker (Ka).  </p>\n<p><img src=\"../../images/shared/Screen_Shot_2020-06-01_at_11.49.56.png\" style=\"width: auto; max-width: 100%; height: auto;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" srcset=\"../../images/shared/Screen_Shot_2020-06-01_at_11.49.56.png?width=1920 1x, ../../images/shared/Screen_Shot_2020-06-01_at_11.49.56.png?width=1920&amp;dpr=2 2x, ../../images/shared/Screen_Shot_2020-06-01_at_11.49.56.png?width=1920&amp;dpr=3 3x\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"../../images/shared/Screen_Shot_2020-06-01_at_11.49.34.png\" style=\"width: auto; max-width: 100%; height: auto;\" class=\"fr-fic fr-dib\" srcset=\"../../images/shared/Screen_Shot_2020-06-01_at_11.49.34.png?width=1920 1x, ../../images/shared/Screen_Shot_2020-06-01_at_11.49.34.png?width=1920&amp;dpr=2 2x, ../../images/shared/Screen_Shot_2020-06-01_at_11.49.34.png?width=1920&amp;dpr=3 3x\"></p>\n<p>You can also download this information here <a class=\"fr-file\" href=\"../../pdfs/shared/interrogatives_(1).pdf\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Interrogatives.pdf</a></p>\n</div>",
